node.text:
Thanks to my friends @amfriendsipo I’m apart of the bedtime and lullaby summer reading series!  Click the link in my bio to register when we go live August 15th!  Shabbat Shalom!
#TheMouseWhoDancedTheHora

node.text:
We’ve been on the grind for many years to get to this point. @rotimi has been singing since he was a child and this picture which is the first time he held a microphone is now the cover of his album that will take you on a musical journey. I’m so proud of him and the work everyone has put in to make this album. August 27th you’ll be able to hear the journey. He’s arrived and here to stay. #AllOrNothing
#FrontRoMusicGroup
#Empire

node.text:
Quick 24 hour trip. Good times in Miami celebrating the CEO and all around great guy @ghazi 💫 I still don’t think he gets the credit he deserves for what he’s done in the music business. He has changed many lives and really cares about the people who work for him and with him. Vibes created by @mshannahkang @mbpevents 🏆🏆🙌🏾
#HappyBirthdayGhazi 
#EMPIRE
